2747
03:30:29,094 --> 03:30:35,078
Finally, as a father, I don't appreciate that these threats have forced me to have to have some uncomfortable conversations with my children and my husband.

2748
03:30:35,399 --> 03:30:39,121
I also, as a Medford resident for 15 years, not that it matters, I agree.

2749
03:30:40,948 --> 03:30:42,829
I've never really even locked my front door.

2750
03:30:43,290 --> 03:30:45,011
Now my doors are locked at all times.

2751
03:30:45,932 --> 03:30:52,056
