Back in early 2000, I was around when there was a serious budget crisis when you were on the school committee council, Falco, and we worked together and we did some unique things to make sure that we mitigated some of the funds that weren't there.

2888
03:42:01,987 --> 03:42:03,768
And we did that by working together.

2889
03:42:04,128 --> 03:42:06,869
We didn't do that by the school committee and the council, not seeing eye to eye.

2890
03:42:07,129 --> 03:42:08,470
We did that by working together.

2891
03:42:08,982 --> 03:42:10,863
