2907
03:42:49,754 --> 03:42:57,860
Going back a number of years, and why I'm speaking is not so much about the meeting method, or that's for you folks to figure out, and so on.

2908
03:42:58,481 --> 03:43:06,187
But what disheartens me is there seems to be a theme of Medford has always been

2909
03:43:06,913 --> 03:43:07,993
a divided place.

2910
03:43:09,594 --> 03:43:16,937
I feel badly for what I heard Mr. Rousseau say about how he doesn't feel safe in his home, and I hope that nobody should feel like that.

2911
03:43:17,697 --> 03:43:19,138
And I feel badly about that.

2912
03:43:20,358 --> 03:43:31,803
But having had the experience of growing up here, I moved out for a little while, and having had the unique experience and pleasure of working on the New Schools Project back in No Longer New Schools,

2913
03:43:32,662 --> 03:43:44,886
back about 15 or 20 years ago now, I had the opportunity to meet thousands and thousands of people, probably as many as the counselors, just because of the nature of the work we did.

2914
03:43:45,727 --> 03:43:59,972
And that experience I had with those people, it fueled the committee's work on the schools, because the unity in the people for common cause, improving their family's life,

2915
03:44:01,055 --> 03:44:06,557
and having good experiences in Medford was just so rewarding to listen to.

2916
03:44:06,697 --> 03:44:11,799
And my experience, yes, it's my past experience, but I trust my instincts.

2917
03:44:12,239 --> 03:44:16,641
And when I meet people in the city, whether they're here as a new resident,

2918
03:44:17,600 --> 03:44:26,968
